"I am not sure, I was to busy fighting. But if he is still on ship, he
will regret it in a few astrominutes." Megatron smile darkly. He opened
another com-link, "Stratus, report."

Motormaster heard the command, but was having problems consentrating on
it. Sinnertwin however, knew not to keep Megatron angry. He began to
dash out of the base.

Wildrider jabbed Astrotrain, "C'mon. We can also introduce Dominjoe and
Blindchaos." he said.
